After training finishes, take screenshots of these 4 charts from your wandb run page:

| Chart | What It Shows | Why Judges Care |
|---|---|---|
| **`rewards/reward_format_compliance/mean`** | Format compliance trend over training | Proves the model learned to output valid JSON |
| **`rewards/reward_environment_execution/mean`** | Environment reward trend | Proves Online RL is working (env.step() in reward loop) |
